The paper discusses a new approach to reinforcement learning, specifically in the context of deep reinforcement learning in the Atari 2600 domain. This suggests that the paper is likely to fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of the Asynchronous Advantage Actor Critic (A3C) algorithm, which is commonly used in robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY).
